{"tid":1748034,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［區選］天盛選區手足聽日請本住良知投票！","createTime":"2019-11-23T13:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T15:57:59.000Z","uid":218005,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"e34d67b49c7af7fdcc79d75d1a4602b6e7afafb8","tid":1748034,"uid":218005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:05:26.000Z","msg":"現任區議員<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">陳思靜</span></strong>自稱中立，但實際就藍到發紫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔單止一次又一次眨低同侮辱手足，就連最基本既地區事務都做唔足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講多無謂，有圖有真相！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fS6nNMY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfS6nNMY.jpg&h=89903e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先講地區事務，條友當正坐喺office就已經係做實事，間唔中坐一日半日又要po facebook大肆宣傳(可以喺佢之前既Facebook post fact check)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n算，都明你要呃選票，但係可唔可以唔好突登痴大大塊Banner喺個濕鳩貨櫃度，然後縮喺入面打機？利申：我自己係天盛人，之前都講過，有事搵條友幫手，條友無理過，係佢班前助手(唔係依家呢班垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)親自上門幫我搞掂，然後條友先施施然上黎搵我合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvD9sQ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvD9sQ8.png&h=c60bef04&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M9DYma9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM9DYma9.png&h=9b99e1f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺第一位手足以死明志之後果晚，心水好撚清既陳議員喺Facebook引用咗段咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事後解釋話咁岩上網見到，咁岩自己慣左用facebook記低見到既資料，咁岩有朋友打電話黎所以唔記得自己po左出黎，之後咁岩訓訓下教突然醒起所以起身del左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽完佢個垃圾解釋，我只想講，手足唔係邪教，真正似邪教果個似係你本人，係咁用啲看似懶有道理既文字去包裝依家既社會現況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sn2Y5Fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsn2Y5Fd.jpg&h=bbb72222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張唔多講啦，自稱以地區為本既陳議員點解會同白衣暴徒王威信一齊投棄票既？投棄票既議只我要黎把撚？中立政黨？我屌你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7vz8JsU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7vz8JsU.png&h=fd8da7fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n借古鑑今唔是咁樣的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成段文字邏輯錯曬，搞清楚孫中山喺革命既角色，同埋睇清楚1912年當代社會基建同革命既聯繫先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jh5LLH7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjh5LLH7.png&h=1c25362e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後，小弟不才，想問下點解唔可以同你談論政治議題？你係民選區議員，如果因為立場唔同而要喺我地個屋苑群組被禁聲，咁你真係同共產黨一樣咁惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得too long didn&rsquo;t read，唔緊要，手足們最緊要搞清楚聽日投票投邊個<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1616b5b61e38bd6b7f77948d35738434790b7236","tid":1748034,"uid":218005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:06:22.000Z","msg":"天盛手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2c46092cb4e9adde470c62afb87273b64916a4","tid":1748034,"uid":95409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:06:41.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"50be22cfaa7be742c5618acb53722f14b5c45ed4","tid":1748034,"uid":218005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11